ont style=&quot;font-size: 9px;&quot;&gt;4) Rename `PSX_ENPA_DATA_TEMP` to `PSX_ENPA_DATA_TRG`&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space-collapse: preserve; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 9px;&quot;&gt;5) Recreate `PSX_ENPA_DATA_TEMP` as an empty clone of `PSX_ENPA_DATA_TRG`.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 9px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;6)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space-collapse: preserve; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif;&quot;&gt;Rebuild the indexes on `PSX_ENPA_DATA_TEMP`&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 9px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space-collapse: preserve; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif;&quot;&gt;7) &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;Update the `psx_prime_eod_counts` table with the processed count. And status in psx_prime_eod_status table.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
